{"pageProps":{"news":{"_id":"5f0533113438f6b6ae3ad4d2","title":"读书会第二期","author":"","digest":"读书会活动第二期---我们一起来看电影吧！","content":"<p><span style=\";font-size: 14px;line-height: 23.3240013122559px;\">读书会活动第二期---我们一起来看电影吧！</span></p><p><br clear=\"all\" style=\";font-size: 14px;line-height: 23.3240013122559px;white-space: normal\"  />大家好，感谢大家对CSSA读书会的支持<br  />希望大家能够来参加我们的第二期活动，在轻松的气氛中观电影，聊时事。</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12.8000001907349px\"><br  /></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">时间：本周六下午2:30</span></p><p>地点：Life Science Building, 会议室A465。</p><p><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/cGcYqtanUytjic1hiauu2bgj2Jq9rOWHTOxn4Ejka26V5DF52EchvBZnjdC9yC8GCH4ZrAib4Nr7R68OvCCJOsT6A/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.6022944550669216\" data-w=\"\"  /><br  /></p><p>注名为 Department of Biological Science 的就是Life Science Building. 黄色笔注明的就是正门。在周末期间，Life Science Building 的正门是锁着的。所以需要有人在正门接应大家。在此感谢贾铮同学自告奋勇。</p><p><br  /></p><p>读书会活动在下午2:30 准时开始，希望大家能够在2:10-2:25之见到达Life Science Building 的正门口。这样接应大家的贾铮同学就可以在活动开始前返回会场。找不到地方的同学请电话联系贾铮 （225）776-7405。谢谢大家的理解和支持。</p><p><br  /></p><p>活动的主题内容 </p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">我们<span class=\"\">读书</span><span class=\"\">会</span>的第二期活动是看电影。五月26日</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">美国最高法院以</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">5比4的多数票裁定同性婚姻在全国范围内合法。有些同学可能对同性恋问题比较关注，有些同学可能有些疑问，所以我们<span class=\"\">读书</span><span class=\"\">会</span>决定借这个机<span class=\"\">会</span>邀请大家一起看一部和同性恋人权有关的纪录片</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">---</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">第八号提案</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\"> 8:The Mormon Proposition</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">主持第二期活动的就是<span class=\"\">会</span>长本人，呵呵。我是心理学专业的，在学习和工作的过程当中接触到了同性恋以及对同性恋持有不同观点的人。我<span class=\"\">会</span>在播放电影前做一个</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">10-15分钟的PPT presentation, 从心理学和政治的角度概括一下同性恋人权问题在美国的发展和现状。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">希望大家过来捧场啊。活动期间我们<span class=\"\">会</span>提供零食和饮料，让大家舒舒服服的看电影。无</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">论你对同性恋问题是否熟悉，或者你的观点如何，都欢迎你来参加我们的活动，和大家一起看电影，一起讨论。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">活动进程如下</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">1， PPT presentation</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">2， 播放电影</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">3， 讨论</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">4， 决定下期活动的主题</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><br  /></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">感谢大家对<span class=\"\">读书</span><span class=\"\">会</span>的支持，</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">CSSA <span class=\"\">读书</span><span class=\"\">会</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">胡媛君</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size: 14px;line-height: 23.3240013122559px;\">-- </span><br style=\";font-size: 14px;line-height: 23.3240013122559px;white-space: normal\"  /></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">---------------------</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">Chinese Student and Scholar Association (CSSA)</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">Louisiana State University (LSU)</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial, sans-serif\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial, sans-serif\">Official E-mail (only): CSSALSU.official@gmail.com</span></strong></p><p><br  /></p><p><br  /></p>","url":"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIwMjAwNDUxMg==&mid=210085772&idx=1&sn=db139995e5ae991412f967dc47154e20#rd","thumb_media_id":"7dV8VNEBhOtLR9fKD3nEx8FWv51Fs_EuMr0ZKgXzp_w","thumb_url":"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/cGcYqtanUytjic1hiauu2bgj2Jq9rOWHTOevNEicKR3JTI3GbjXYsicACuIk3Fyg7LaX2c09Lczvr6yWqBibLI9fQ8A/0?wx_fmt=jpeg","update_time":"2015-07-08T13:42:10.000Z","media_id":"7dV8VNEBhOtLR9fKD3nEx6d4C2UK4PVH5ICabs85L_0","createdAt":"2020-07-08T02:44:33.084Z","updatedAt":"2020-07-08T02:44:38.555Z","__v":0,"thumb_media":{"_id":"5f0533163438f6b6ae3ad4d3","name":"202067-46766-1tm5m89","alternativeText":null,"caption":null,"hash":"202067_46766_1tm5m89_53beacb759","ext":".jpeg","mime":"image/jpeg","size":44.55,"width":1024,"height":576,"url":"/uploads/202067_46766_1tm5m89_53beacb759.jpeg","formats":{"thumbnail":{"hash":"thumbnail_202067_46766_1tm5m89_53beacb759","ext":".jpeg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":245,"height":138,"size":5.31,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/thumbnail_202067_46766_1tm5m89_53beacb759.jpeg"},"large":{"hash":"large_202067_46766_1tm5m89_53beacb759","ext":".jpeg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":1000,"height":563,"size":42.64,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/large_202067_46766_1tm5m89_53beacb759.jpeg"},"medium":{"hash":"medium_202067_46766_1tm5m89_53beacb759","ext":".jpeg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":750,"height":422,"size":27.76,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/medium_202067_46766_1tm5m89_53beacb759.jpeg"},"small":{"hash":"small_202067_46766_1tm5m89_53beacb759","ext":".jpeg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":500,"height":281,"size":15.47,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/small_202067_46766_1tm5m89_53beacb759.jpeg"}},"provider":"local","related":["5f0533113438f6b6ae3ad4d2"],"createdAt":"2020-07-08T02:44:38